Text: it's time for my periodic expression of gratitude to you VTV...  THANK YOU... you make my evenings with the wife more bearable...  :-)  CHEERS!

Thanks for no longer using Lavf53.2.0 and going back to Transcode-1.0.6. The audio should now play on hardware media players that couldn't handle the non-standard VBR audio produced by Lavf. 
Thanks again.
